This is some info for dummies (like me after holidays) how to use this testbench
explaining why there are so many files and etc

(the paths which are absolute, are that of my PC, sorry, but they can be useful)


WR FEC is a forward error correction in White Rabbit IP core to encode and decode data.
STATUS:
- we have FEC encoder working in HW [not fully debugged]: wr_fec_en.vhd
- we haven't got decoder in HW. however, we have one in SW, it's used for tests
TODO:
- debug FEC encoder
- write FEC decoder

>>>>>>>>>>>> General WR FEC design <<<<<<<<<<<<<<<

               wr_fec.vhd           <---             wr_fec_pck.vhd
         [top entity, not existing]    [ready, all the components and constants]
              /           \
             /             \
            /               \
      wr_fec_de.vhd         wr_fec_en.vhd   
[decoder, note ready]         [ready]
                            /           \
                           /             \
                          /               \
            wr_fec_en_interface.vhd   wr_fec_engine.vhd
                                     /     |      \
                                    /      |       \
                                   /       |        \
    parameters.vhd --> RS_erasure.vhd     RAMs    wr_hamming_pkg.vhd <-- hamm_packge_64bit.vhd
                                      [embedded memory ]
                                      /     |      |  \
                                     /      |      |   \
                                    /       |      |    \
                                   /   PAYLOAD_1   |  RS_PAYLOAD
                                HEADER          PAYLOAD_1 


>>>>>>>>>>>> WR FEC encoder testing design <<<<<<<<<<<<<<<
   input:                                             output:
  Wishbone                                       Fabrick Interface [wrf]
[control gen]                                     [frames, data stream]
   |                                                   / \
   |               wr_fec_and_gen_with_wrf.vhd          |
   |           /               |               \        |
   |          /                |                \       |
  \ /        /      [wbp]      |         [wbp]   \      |
wr_fec_dummy_gen.vhd ---> wr_fec_en.vhd  ----> wr_fec_wb_to_wrf.vhd 
            |           [Unite under test]         
            |
            |
    wr_fec_dummy_gen_if.vhd
[      Wishbone interface generated     ]
[ with wbgen2:                          ]
[ - src : wr_fec_dummy_pck_gen_if.wb    ]
[ - info: wr_fec_dummy_pck_gen_if.html  ]




TREE
                           [top entities]
|-- wr_fec_and_gen.vhd               - fec encoder with dummy frames generator (WBp output)
|-- wr_fec_and_gen_with_wrf.vhd      - fec encoder with dummy frames generator and converter to 
|                                      Fabric interface for output

                        [dummy frame generator]
|-- wr_fec_dummy_pck_gen.vhd         - dummy frame generator
|-- wr_fec_dummy_pck_gen_if.html     - layout of the registers controlling frames generator
|-- wr_fec_dummy_pck_gen_if.vhd      - Wishbone interace to control frames generator
|-- wr_fec_dummy_pck_gen_if.wb       - lua script to generate frames genertor's WB interface 
|                                      using wbgen2 (http://www.ohwr.org/projects/wishbone-gen)

                           [FEC encoder]
|-- wr_fec_en_engine.vhd             - FEC encoder engine
|-- wr_fec_en_interface.vhd          - FEC encoder interface
|-- wr_fec_en.vhd                    - Fevn encoder top entity

                          [hamming decoder/encoder]
|-- hamm_package_64bit.vhd           - used by hamming encoder/decodeer
|-- wr_hamming_pkg.vhd               - Hamming package

                         [RS encoder/decocer]
|-- gf256-pkg.vhd                    - used by RS encoder/decodre
|-- parameters.vhd                   - settings of RS encodr/decoder
|-- RS_erasure.vhd                   - Reed-Solomon encoder/decoder

                        [FEC decoder]
|-- wr_fec_de.vhd                    - [unfinished] FEC decoder top entity
|-- wr_fec_de_engine.vhd             - [unfinished] FEC decoder engine
|-- wr_fec_de_interface.vhd          - [unfinished] FEC decoder interface

                        [ohter staff]
|-- wr_fec_pkg.vhd                   - FEC package
|-- FECencoding.jpg
|-- Manifest.py                     
|-- README
|-- wr_fec_wb_to_wrf.vhd             - converter from Wishbone pipelined to Fabric Interface (WBP->WRF)



